| EventLoopFutureWait.swift:20:17:20:29 | call to wait() | Calling wait() on an EventLoopFuture blocks the current thread. On an EventLoop thread this causes a deadlock; off-loop it wastes resources. Use NIOAsyncChannel and await results in a structured async context instead. |
